                "@type": "Person",
                "name": "Kimberly"
            },
            "reviewBody": "This is an excellent recipe. I've tried tons of different gluten-free flour combos and this one really hits the mark. The waffles turned out light and crispy. I think the secret is in letting the batter sit once all the ingredients have been combined to all the flours to absorb the liquids fully. Really happy with the results. Bravo!"
        },
        {
            "@type": "Review",
