            },
            "reviewBody": "Tried this recipe and it did not go well. The batter seemed very thin. It took much longer to cook and tended to stick to the waffle iron. While most of the waffles can out in messy sections the taste was not bad. Taste was a bit sweeter than traditional waffles but still not bad."
